When you start the [[Mysterious Island Quest]], you will get a different set of adventures from the normal [[The Hippy Camp|Hippy Camp]]. The Hippies will be gearing up for full-scale war against the Frat Boys.

Once the war starts, the [[The Hippy Camp (Wartime)|Hippy Camp]] becomes a place to purchase Hippy War Gear and serves as headquarters for [[The Big Wisniewski]]. 

